    "title": "ci: Test with unreleased / experimental / nightly compilers",
    "body": "If we do this, we can catch issues like the recent constant-time problem early enough. I already had some local notes on this. Here's a list of helpful resources for Debian:\r\n\r\n* https://wiki.debian.org/DebianExperimental\r\n  * https://packages.debian.org/experimental/clang-17\r\n  * https://packages.debian.org/de/experimental/gcc-13\r\n* https://jwakely.github.io/pkg-gcc-latest/\r\n* https://apt.llvm.org/\r\n",
